nodes.name: Bran comes of age
nodes.desc: Bran climbs walls, gets pushed from window and crippled, and helps manage Winterfell while Robb is away. He dreams of three-eyed crows

nodes.name: Arya comes of age
nodes.desc: Arya wants to be a soldier, Jon gives her Needle, she beats Joffrey in a fight, learns how to swordfight and is found by Yoren who tries to take her back to Winterfell

nodes.name: Sansa coming of age
nodes.desc: Sansa is betrothed to Joffrey, she really wants to be queen, she has a special relationship with Sandor Clegane, she is held prisoner by the Lannisters.

nodes.name: Catelyn hates Jon Snow
nodes.desc: Catelyn resents Jon Snow for being Ned's bastard. She won't let him join the King's feast in Winterfell and is upset when he says goodbye to Bran.

nodes.name: Starks find direwolves
nodes.desc: Direwolves grow up in Winterfell nad protect the Stark children. They often intervene when trouble is brewing.

nodes.name: Jon Arryn is murdered
nodes.desc: Jon Arryne was the hand of the king

nodes.name: Cersei & Jaime are in love
nodes.desc: They murder Jon Arryn to cover up their secret. Jaime pushed Bran for seeing them together. Joffrey is not the rightful air.  Jon Arryn's squire is murdered in the tournament to cover up the murder of Jon Arryn. Cersei makes Jaime the head of the King's Guard

nodes.name: Robert Baratheon is king
nodes.desc: Robert goes to Winterfell to ask Ned to be his hand, returns, orders an assassination of Daenarys Targaryen. Sleeps with prostitues and Gendry is his oldest bastard.

nodes.name: Ned becomes hand of the king
nodes.desc: Ned accepts the offer to be hand of the king. Then he quits is rehired, summons Tywin to pay for Gregor Clegane's crimes, declares Stannis as true king, buys the city watch from Baelish, is crossed, and is murdered.

nodes.name: Joffrey coming of age
nodes.desc: Joffrey is betrothed to Sansa, attacked butcher's boy, and is (unrightful) heir to the throne, takes the throne and kills Ned Stark

nodes.name: King is in love with Lyanna (dead)
Robert and Ned grew up together
Previous war in Westeros
nodes.desc: Robert killed Rhaegar Targaryen and Jaime Lannister killed Aerys Targaryen

nodes.name: Daenarys coming of age
nodes.desc: She weds Khal Drogo, recieves Dragon eggs,becomes one of the Dothraki people, gets pregnant, and hatches dragons.

nodes.name: Viserys plots against Westeros
nodes.desc: He forces Daenarys to wed Khal Drogo, he wants to use Drogo's army to take over Westeros, and is horrible to Daenarys.

nodes.name: Uncle Benjin arrives from the wall
Jon Snow coming of age
nodes.desc: He takes the Black for honor, asks Ned about his mom, is a virgin, becomes Commander Mormont's steward, recieves Long Claw and goes on a raid beyond the wall.

nodes.name: Lysa Arryn fled to the Eyrie
nodes.desc: She brought her son Robyn Arryn.

nodes.name: Ned's father was the hand of the king
nodes.desc: He was murdered in King's Landing with Ned's brother

nodes.name: Jorah Mormont meets Daenarys
nodes.desc: He pledges fielty to Daenarys and helps her adjust to the Dothraki way of living. Fled Westeros because he sold poacher.

nodes.name: Tyrion goes to The Wall
nodes.desc: He goes to the wall with Jon, they bond, on his way back he is arrested by Catelyn and taken to the Eryie, he is pardoned and meets up with wildlings and then his father in battle where he meets Shae. He is made temporary Hand of the King.

nodes.name: Cersei and Robert lost a child
Robb coming of age
nodes.desc: He takes care of winterfell, goes to war, declared king, and captures Jaime Lannister.

nodes.name: Catelyn avenges Bran's attacker
nodes.desc: Catelyn is attacked, blames Lannisters for pushing Bran off a wall, she visits King's Landing, arrests Tyrion and take him to the Eyrie.

nodes.name: Tournament in Ned's honor
nodes.desc: Ned won't let Robert Baratheon fight in the tournament. The knight of flowers (Ser Loras) beats Gregor Clegane for gold and Sandor defends Loras.

nodes.name: Cersei is obsessed with power
nodes.desc: Cersei tries to control Robert Baratheon and later Joffrey on the throne. She has an affair with Lancel Lannister, squire of the King to have him murder Robert.

nodes.name: Lord Baelish is obsessed with power
nodes.desc: He has had a life-long crush on Catelyn Tully, he is power hungry and takes a liking to Sansa

nodes.name: Robert tells story about his first kill
Uncle Benjin goes on a raid
Commander Mormont needs recruits
nodes.desc: Commander Mormont asks Tyrion for more men and tells him to ask his sister, Cersei.

nodes.name: Theon Greyjoy is held captive
nodes.desc: Theon Gregjoy is held captive at Winterfell because of his father's rebellion

nodes.name: Sam Tarly coming of age
nodes.desc: Sam Tarley is forced to take the black, he arrives at the wall, befriends Jon Snow, becomes Maester Amon's steward

nodes.name: Dragon skulls in Kings Landing
nodes.desc: Viserys talks about this to Doreah

nodes.name: The wildlings have a leader
nodes.desc: The wildlings follow a king beyond the wall, Mance Rayder.

nodes.name: Clegane Brother's history
nodes.desc: Gregor Clegane burned Sandor Clegane's face into a fire as a kid

nodes.name: Bron meets Tyrion
nodes.desc: Bron is introduced to Tyrion and becomes his sellsword, he defends him in front of Lysa Arryn, he goes to Tywin's camp and then King's Landing

nodes.name: Lancel Lannister is King's Squire
nodes.desc: It is revealed that he is sleeping with Cersie and gave Robert Baratheon the poisoned wine that killed him. He is later made a knight.

nodes.name: Renly and Ser Loras in love
nodes.desc: Renly and Ser Loras like each other. Loras convinces Renly he should be king.

nodes.name: Varys warns Ned
nodes.desc: Varys warns Ned of Robert's impending doom

nodes.name: Arya eavesdrops
nodes.desc: Arya overhears Varys and Illryo  plotting against the throne

nodes.name: Yoren goes south
nodes.desc: Yoren asks Ned for recruits for the wall, tells him about Tyrion's arrest. He finds Arya and hides her in his recruits to take her home safely

nodes.name: Robert is  murdered
nodes.desc: Robert Baratheon goes on a hunting trip and is killed by a boar. His squire gave him poisoned wine.

nodes.name: Jaime attacks Ned
nodes.desc: Jaime attacks Ned for Catelyn arresting Tyrion

nodes.name: Gregor Clegane raids villages
nodes.desc: Gregor Clegane raids villages to get Tyrion back from the Starks

nodes.name: Tywin Lannister goes to war
nodes.desc: He orders Jamie to take an army to Riverrun. Jaime is captured.

nodes.name: Lannisters fight city watch men
nodes.desc: Tywin Lannister goes to war against Starks to get Tyrion back. He is made hand of the king

nodes.name: Catelyn asks for Lord Frey's help
nodes.desc: Catelyn asks for Lord Frey's help and betrothes Arya and Rob to Frey's children.

nodes.name: Amon Targaryen is the Maester of the Wall
Khal Drogo Dies
nodes.desc: Drogo is stabbed in a fight, a witch tries to heal him. He dies.

nodes.name: Gendry goes to The Wall
nodes.desc: King Robert's bastard goes north to the wall with Yoren & Arya

nodes.name: Night's Watch go on a raid
nodes.desc: A large party of the Nigh's Watch ride north to fight walkers and wildlings
